{ KBUILD_DEFCONFIG #linux-KBUILD_DEFCONFIG

 `arch/$SRCARCH/Makefile` is → https://github.com/torvalds/linux/blob/f291209eca5eba0b4704fa0832af57b12dbc1a02/Makefile#L687-L691[included] from the main `→ Linux/kernel/source/Makefile` to set and export the variable `KBUILD_DEFCONFIG`.

 `→ Linux/kernel/source/scripts/kconfig/Makefile` → https://github.com/torvalds/linux/blob/f291209eca5eba0b4704fa0832af57b12dbc1a02/scripts/kconfig/Makefile#L28[adds] the value of `KBUILD_DEFCONFIG` to `KCONFIG_DEFCONFIG_LIST`.

  `KBUILD_DEFCONFIG` is used for `→ Linux/kernel/compilation/make/defconfig`.

